  |                                                                         |
  |     Summary                                                             |
  |   -------------------------------------------------------------------   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Big Crown: Showdown sees friends become foes as they compete for      |
  |   the crown in 4-player local and online multiplayer combat, set over   |
  |   3 wacky worlds full of medieval shenanigans. Avoid perilous hazards   |
  |   and engage in frantic fights as you attempt to knock your opponents   |
  |   off 15 crazy courses in the ultimate royal battle!                    |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Pick Up and Play Combat: Big Crown Showdown is an accessible and    |
  |     enjoyable experience for players of all ages and skill levels.      |
  |     The one-button combat provides a true 'pick up and play'            |
  |     experience whilst still containing enough depth for players to      |
  |     come back for more                                                  |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Non-Stop Camera: Big Crown Showdown uses a unique camera system     |
  |     that moves along the track in a constant motion, forcing players    |
  |     to keep moving forward into new challenges. There's no time rest    |
  |     when the camera keeps the action going                              |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Classic Platforming: It's not all about combat in Big Crown         |
  |     Showdown. The game blends chaotic combat with sections of tricky    |
  |     platforming, challenging players to move fast and react quickly.    |
  |     Every track has a number of deadly obstacles for players to avoid   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Languages: English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Portuguese,     |
  |   Russian, Japanese and Chinese.                                        |
